5.Cook personally knows the judge that approved my C.O. was a left wing liberal. Really? Sorry, it was Draft Board #125 of Long Beach California. You just lied Cook. You stated it was a judge. It was a draft board.  So who is lying now folks?? When will you folks stand up to the lying bully?<br>
6. The C.O. status does not exempt you from the shame and pain you feel&quot; speaks Cook again.  WRONG. I feel no shame, I am proud of what &quot;I did during the war daddy&quot;. I feel no shame, no pain, only anger and frustration at those who are led by the nose, esp. by such a crock of shit as Cook. Again, he is lying. Will none of you call him on this?<br>
7. Apologize for not having gone? Jesus, I thank GOD that I did not go every day.As far as I am concerned, not going was the best thing that could ever have happened to me. So once again, COOK IS LYING. Hey Tom, how come Cook can lie and lie, and you remain silent, but I bend the truth once, and you are up my A**?  Think about it Tom.<br><br>
Cook, you know you love me. I give your hatred and racism a face to attack. You are the sick puppy here. To bad none of your wantabe Native American's and HeliPilots have the balls to tell you to your face.  First you say your are a veteran Riverside Cop, remember?, now you say you are a Los Angeles Cop, See what I mean?  And your playtoys say nothing.<br><br>
